1
00:00:43,010 --> 00:00:46,220
♪Pink hands so fine♪

2
00:00:46,580 --> 00:00:49,440
♪Gold-branded wine♪

3
00:00:50,230 --> 00:00:55,680
♪Spring paints willows green;
palace walls can't confine♪

4
00:00:57,360 --> 00:01:00,820
♪East wind unfair♪

5
00:01:01,010 --> 00:01:04,000
♪Happy times rare♪

6
00:01:04,540 --> 00:01:07,810
♪In my heart, sad thoughts throng♪

7
00:01:08,050 --> 00:01:11,360
♪We've severed for years long♪

8
00:01:11,580 --> 00:01:17,120
♪Wrong, wrong, wrong♪

9
00:01:30,900 --> 00:01:35,180
=Si Jin=

10
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:39,180
=Episode 33=

11
00:01:39,180 --> 00:01:41,430
(Tiande Hall)

12
00:01:41,430 --> 00:01:42,430
Everyone,

13
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:44,670
is there anything else to report?

14
00:01:45,950 --> 00:01:46,870
Your Majesty,

15
00:01:47,510 --> 00:01:49,950
I, Zhen Heng, have a matter to report.

16
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,560
Prince Yan...

17
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:04,790
Since there is nothing else,

18
00:02:05,350 --> 00:02:06,280
let's dismiss the court.

19
00:02:08,030 --> 00:02:09,990
The court is dismissed.

20
00:02:10,710 --> 00:02:13,080
I take my leave.

21
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,040
Mr. Zhen.

22
00:02:25,590 --> 00:02:26,510
You may leave.

23
00:02:35,750 --> 00:02:37,200
I take my leave.

24
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,200
Your Majesty,

25
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:50,810
if he keeps kneeling like this,

26
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,360
how will he get married?

27
00:02:53,030 --> 00:02:54,640
Even if I let him go,

28
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,110
he won't agree to it.

29
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:59,480
Doesn't he want to die?

30
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:03,110
Fine, let him be.

31
00:03:03,470 --> 00:03:05,080
Let him kneel for a few more days.

32
00:03:05,470 --> 00:03:06,510
Once the time comes,

33
00:03:07,150 --> 00:03:08,430
send him straight to the wedding.

34
00:03:21,030 --> 00:03:21,960
Jin, I understand

35
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:22,950
your thoughts,

36
00:03:26,430 --> 00:03:27,980
but an imperial edict cannot be defied.

37
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:08,760
Miss, Miss Chuchu is here.

38
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,680
One is starving in the Palace;

39
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:13,830
the other is starving here.

40
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,440
Isn't that exactly

41
00:04:15,590 --> 00:04:16,880
what Cui Mingyue wants?

42
00:04:21,310 --> 00:04:22,640
Come on, eat something.

43
00:04:23,070 --> 00:04:23,990
Chuchu,

44
00:04:24,510 --> 00:04:25,890
is there truly no one in the Palace

45
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:29,120
who can help him?

46
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,760
What should I do?

47
00:04:32,870 --> 00:04:33,910
What should I do?

48
00:04:41,300 --> 00:04:43,380
(Grand Princess's Mansion)

49
00:04:43,390 --> 00:04:44,240
Your Grace,

50
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:46,350
this is the wedding robe
from the Palace.

51
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,680
Is this for the Princess Consort?

52
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,040
Yes.

53
00:04:57,190 --> 00:04:59,200
So, Jiang Si's attire
is the same as mine?

54
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,590
It should be.

55
00:05:00,950 --> 00:05:02,100
How could she deserve to wear

56
00:05:02,170 --> 00:05:04,330
(Dignified and Delicate)
the same wedding dress as me?

57
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:06,960
Mother,

58
00:05:07,110 --> 00:05:08,390
at the blossom-viewing banquet,

59
00:05:08,390 --> 00:05:10,000
Jiang Si already imitated my outfit.

60
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:10,920
On my wedding day,

61
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,640
I cannot suffer such humiliation.

62
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,630
Have the embroiderers

63
00:05:15,630 --> 00:05:17,150
alter this wedding robe.

64
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:19,760
Use the jewels bestowed by His Majesty

65
00:05:19,870 --> 00:05:21,030
to decorate it further.

66
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,160
Yes.

67
00:05:23,950 --> 00:05:25,830
Mother, you are the best.

68
00:05:26,750 --> 00:05:28,200
Are you happy now?

69
00:05:30,660 --> 00:05:33,860
(Zhuque Gate)

70
00:05:33,870 --> 00:05:34,450
Miss,

71
00:05:34,450 --> 00:05:35,590
Mr. Zhen said he'd inform us

72
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,080
as soon as there is news.

73
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,640
Let's go home and wait.

74
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:44,950
It's fine. I'll wait here.

75
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:52,320
♪The world is changing;
may we find where we belong♪

76
00:05:53,340 --> 00:05:59,400
♪I want nothing else; I'll stop for you♪

77
00:06:00,220 --> 00:06:05,910
♪I'll give up everything♪

78
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:12,560
♪To write to you,
a few words make a book♪

79
00:06:14,340 --> 00:06:19,580
♪Mottled fate reaches the end♪

80
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,440
There is no need to reconsider.

81
00:06:21,870 --> 00:06:23,560
This is my final answer.

82
00:06:24,950 --> 00:06:27,000
Giving all six flowers to one lady

83
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:29,800
is something I wanted to do

84
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:31,270
but I didn't dare.

85
00:06:33,970 --> 00:06:37,390
♪Looking back, everything is♪

86
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:40,280
♪Difficult to untangle♪

87
00:06:40,860 --> 00:06:45,990
♪All is to guard my love for you♪

88
00:06:47,740 --> 00:06:51,230
♪Morning mist’s reduced to dew♪

89
00:06:51,230 --> 00:06:54,220
♪The sun rises as usual♪

90
00:06:54,600 --> 00:07:00,160
♪In this lifetime,
I only want to be with you♪

91
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:21,160
♪To write to you,
a few words make a book♪

92
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,940
(Tiande Hall)

93
00:07:22,940 --> 00:07:28,180
♪Mottled fate reaches the end♪

94
00:07:29,370 --> 00:07:35,500
♪Hope to embrace eternity with you♪

95
00:07:35,770 --> 00:07:41,860
♪As if in a dream,
petals fall on the paper♪

96
00:07:42,570 --> 00:07:45,990
♪Looking back, everything is♪

97
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:48,990
♪The sun rises as usual♪

98
00:07:56,270 --> 00:07:58,120
Jin, have some water.

99
00:07:58,830 --> 00:08:00,760
No.

100
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:02,560
I asked Mother

101
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:03,880
to plead with Father,

102
00:08:04,190 --> 00:08:05,640
but he refused.

103
00:08:06,750 --> 00:08:09,150
I already guessed as much.

104
00:08:32,670 --> 00:08:34,040
In the blink of an eye,

105
00:08:34,670 --> 00:08:36,830
Princess Mingyue is about to marry.

106
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:40,160
Two hairpins on one head?

107
00:08:40,630 --> 00:08:41,870
Isn't that too much?

108
00:08:45,870 --> 00:08:47,160
Then I'll wear just one.

109
00:08:47,550 --> 00:08:48,680
Mother, don't worry.

110
00:08:49,030 --> 00:08:50,550
Let Jiang Si

111
00:08:50,550 --> 00:08:51,570
enjoy her moment for now.

112
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,150
After the wedding,

113
00:08:53,150 --> 00:08:54,320
under the same roof,

114
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,680
I'll make sure to get rid of her.

115
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,080
Is Jiang Si

116
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,920
that easy to deal with?

117
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:02,870
Mother, you overestimate her.

118
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,160
Look.

119
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:06,040
Once Uncle's decree is issued,

120
00:09:06,150 --> 00:09:07,680
won't she have to obey?

121
00:09:08,510 --> 00:09:10,200
After the wedding,

122
00:09:10,630 --> 00:09:11,550
I don't believe

123
00:09:11,690 --> 00:09:13,440
that Yu Jin will protect her every day.

124
00:09:13,790 --> 00:09:16,200
You are too naive.

125
00:09:21,510 --> 00:09:22,430
Mr. Zhen.

126
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:24,080
Mr. Zhen.

127
00:09:24,870 --> 00:09:25,790
Miss Jiang,

128
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:27,320
you look a bit weary.

129
00:09:28,260 --> 00:09:29,580
Please take care of yourself.

130
00:09:32,700 --> 00:09:33,940
Even I did not expect

131
00:09:34,660 --> 00:09:35,580
that Prince Yan

132
00:09:35,940 --> 00:09:37,420
would risk his life to defy the edict.

133
00:09:37,660 --> 00:09:38,700
His devotion is unwavering.

134
00:09:40,340 --> 00:09:41,740
Miss Jiang, your heart remains

135
00:09:42,260 --> 00:09:43,740
with him even outside the Palace.

136
00:09:44,540 --> 00:09:45,660
Through trials and hardships,

137
00:09:45,660 --> 00:09:46,580
you stand by his side.

138
00:09:47,060 --> 00:09:49,060
I truly admire you.

139
00:09:52,060 --> 00:09:52,980
Miss Jiang,

140
00:09:54,020 --> 00:09:55,540
even these towering walls

141
00:09:56,380 --> 00:09:58,020
can't keep apart

142
00:09:58,460 --> 00:09:59,660
your love for each other.

143
00:10:04,860 --> 00:10:05,780
Take care.

144
00:10:19,940 --> 00:10:21,820
Jin's condition is very bad.

145
00:10:22,500 --> 00:10:23,940
I've tried many ways,

146
00:10:24,100 --> 00:10:26,040
but I don't know
how to help him and Miss Jiang.

147
00:10:27,140 --> 00:10:28,140
Mr. Zhen,

148
00:10:28,140 --> 00:10:29,700
you are their close friend,

149
00:10:29,900 --> 00:10:31,020
so you must understand them.

150
00:10:32,140 --> 00:10:33,780
Do you have any way

151
00:10:33,780 --> 00:10:34,780
to help them

152
00:10:35,140 --> 00:10:36,140
meet each other?

153
00:10:44,260 --> 00:10:45,180
Your Highness,

154
00:10:46,020 --> 00:10:48,500
how about using a kite?

155
00:10:49,100 --> 00:10:50,060
A kite?

156
00:10:55,740 --> 00:10:56,660
Miss Jiang.

157
00:10:56,780 --> 00:10:57,700
Ms. Hua.

158
00:10:57,860 --> 00:10:59,500
The Empress has sent me to escort you

159
00:10:59,740 --> 00:11:01,140
to the Imperial Garden for a stroll.

160
00:11:03,940 --> 00:11:04,860
Alright.

161
00:11:05,860 --> 00:11:06,780
Help Miss Jiang.

162
00:11:07,260 --> 00:11:08,220
I'll stay here.

163
00:11:28,180 --> 00:11:29,020
Your Highness.

164
00:11:29,020 --> 00:11:30,660
Greetings, Your Highness.

165
00:11:32,260 --> 00:11:33,780
Miss Jiang, you may not know

166
00:11:33,780 --> 00:11:35,700
why I summoned you here.

167
00:11:39,020 --> 00:11:39,940
Come here.

168
00:11:41,860 --> 00:11:44,980
Though the Imperial Garden
is in the inner Palace,

169
00:11:45,900 --> 00:11:47,500
it is just one wall away

170
00:11:47,940 --> 00:11:49,340
from the Tiande Hall.

171
00:11:50,660 --> 00:11:52,580
This is the closest you can get to him.

172
00:11:57,540 --> 00:11:58,540
Thank you, Your Highness.

173
00:12:24,620 --> 00:12:25,620
Jin,

174
00:12:25,620 --> 00:12:27,340
you've been kneeling for three days.

175
00:12:27,580 --> 00:12:29,160
Father hasn't relented in the slightest.

176
00:12:29,340 --> 00:12:30,660
Are you going to keep kneeling?

177
00:12:31,460 --> 00:12:32,380
Yes.

178
00:12:32,860 --> 00:12:33,780
If you keep kneeling,

179
00:12:33,780 --> 00:12:35,180
your body will collapse.

180
00:12:39,980 --> 00:12:40,860
Have you forgotten

181
00:12:40,860 --> 00:12:42,100
who you are?

182
00:12:42,740 --> 00:12:44,540
If I can't even control my son,

183
00:12:44,540 --> 00:12:45,580
how can I rule my country?

184
00:12:45,780 --> 00:12:46,700
(Father,)

185
00:12:47,100 --> 00:12:48,980
(I have never forgotten who I am.)

186
00:12:49,460 --> 00:12:50,540
(I also understand)

187
00:12:50,540 --> 00:12:51,700
(that as Emperor,)

188
00:12:51,700 --> 00:12:53,060
(you cannot take back your edict.)

189
00:12:53,060 --> 00:12:55,220
(But I only love Jiang Si.)

190
00:12:55,580 --> 00:12:56,500
Jin,

191
00:12:57,860 --> 00:12:58,980
do you miss Miss Jiang?

192
00:13:03,980 --> 00:13:04,900
Of course.

193
00:13:11,460 --> 00:13:12,380
Jin, look.

194
00:13:13,060 --> 00:13:13,980
Look over there.

195
00:13:16,660 --> 00:13:17,700
Miss Jiang is right there.

196
00:13:18,020 --> 00:13:19,240
She's been with you all along.

197
00:13:35,540 --> 00:13:37,270
♪From place to place♪

198
00:13:37,270 --> 00:13:41,690
♪I drift in the world alone♪

199
00:13:42,580 --> 00:13:44,480
♪The cool breeze comes and goes♪

200
00:13:44,500 --> 00:13:46,580
I know that after I become Prince Yan,

201
00:13:47,580 --> 00:13:49,500
the road ahead will be even harder.

202
00:13:50,060 --> 00:13:51,700
I don't deserve what you want,

203
00:13:52,380 --> 00:13:54,300
a small courtyard, a plot of land.

204
00:13:54,860 --> 00:13:56,220
But I have made up my mind.

205
00:13:56,460 --> 00:13:57,580
This life, I'll cling to you.

206
00:13:57,580 --> 00:13:58,780
You can't drive me away.

207
00:14:00,020 --> 00:14:02,860
I was born and raised in Dazhou.

208
00:14:03,460 --> 00:14:04,740
How could I not love it?

209
00:14:06,140 --> 00:14:07,540
But I like

210
00:14:09,140 --> 00:14:10,860
living with you even more.

211
00:14:13,910 --> 00:14:15,690
♪Time glows♪

212
00:14:15,690 --> 00:14:19,820
♪Together, we'll see light♪

213
00:14:20,170 --> 00:14:23,260
♪And stars♪

214
00:14:25,620 --> 00:14:27,100
Take a look! Sugar figures!

215
00:14:27,100 --> 00:14:28,700
- Mother.
- Pick one yourself.

216
00:14:28,700 --> 00:14:30,140
I want a sugar figure.

217
00:14:32,780 --> 00:14:33,700
Which one do you want?

218
00:14:33,900 --> 00:14:35,540
Alright, choose one.

219
00:14:35,540 --> 00:14:37,140
- Which one?
- I want the little rabbit.

220
00:14:37,420 --> 00:14:38,340
The little rabbit.

221
00:14:38,660 --> 00:14:39,580
Sir, how much?

222
00:14:39,780 --> 00:14:40,700
Two wen.

223
00:14:40,820 --> 00:14:41,740
Alright.

224
00:14:45,060 --> 00:14:45,980
Thank you, Ma'am.

225
00:14:46,180 --> 00:14:47,100
Thank you.

226
00:14:50,500 --> 00:14:51,460
Father.

227
00:15:00,180 --> 00:15:01,260
Mother,

228
00:15:02,140 --> 00:15:04,220
is that Father?

229
00:15:04,780 --> 00:15:06,420
Yan, you're mistaken.

230
00:15:07,140 --> 00:15:08,220
That is not your father.

231
00:15:09,020 --> 00:15:09,940
Let's go home.

232
00:15:23,540 --> 00:15:25,460
(Morning Drizzle)

233
00:15:25,460 --> 00:15:26,500
Hold on tight, Yan.

234
00:15:26,500 --> 00:15:27,420
Sure.

235
00:15:34,660 --> 00:15:35,580
Mother,

236
00:15:36,580 --> 00:15:38,180
was that man I just saw

237
00:15:38,780 --> 00:15:40,060
my father?

238
00:15:42,180 --> 00:15:43,100
No.

239
00:15:43,340 --> 00:15:44,420
He's just a madman.

240
00:17:02,580 --> 00:17:04,460
Thank you, Ma'am. Thank you.

241
00:17:04,660 --> 00:17:05,580
Zhu Ziyu.

242
00:17:12,700 --> 00:17:14,980
It's not me. You have the wrong man.

243
00:17:21,340 --> 00:17:22,780
How did you end up like this?

244
00:17:31,460 --> 00:17:33,060
Not long after our divorce,

245
00:17:35,060 --> 00:17:36,860
my family was confiscated and exiled.

246
00:17:37,580 --> 00:17:39,260
On the way, the Grand Princess

247
00:17:40,020 --> 00:17:42,300
sent people to silence us.

248
00:17:43,780 --> 00:17:46,180
83 people of my family

249
00:17:47,980 --> 00:17:50,300
were slaughtered on the road.

250
00:17:52,460 --> 00:17:53,620
I was the only one

251
00:17:53,620 --> 00:17:55,060
who survived.

252
00:18:05,980 --> 00:18:08,420
You should never have trusted
Cui Mingyue.

253
00:18:09,500 --> 00:18:10,900
Day and night,

254
00:18:13,500 --> 00:18:15,780
I have been tormented by guilt,
wishing for death.

255
00:18:16,700 --> 00:18:17,780
But I know

256
00:18:18,340 --> 00:18:20,220
I do not deserve release.

257
00:18:21,300 --> 00:18:23,460
I must suffer through regret

258
00:18:25,820 --> 00:18:26,740
to atone for my sins.

259
00:18:32,540 --> 00:18:34,020
Those two have always been ruthless.

260
00:18:36,220 --> 00:18:37,580
You were not their only victim.

261
00:18:39,100 --> 00:18:40,220
My mother was also killed

262
00:18:43,100 --> 00:18:44,820
by the Grand Princess.

263
00:18:46,460 --> 00:18:48,980
And now they want to ruin Si's marriage.

264
00:18:49,900 --> 00:18:52,460
Cui Mingyue destroyed your family,

265
00:18:53,980 --> 00:18:56,220
and now she'll become Princess Yan.

266
00:18:57,420 --> 00:18:59,660
They are so cruel and heartless.

267
00:19:01,100 --> 00:19:02,380
Must we rely on heaven

268
00:19:02,380 --> 00:19:03,420
to punish them?

269
00:19:05,060 --> 00:19:05,980
Azhu.

270
00:19:09,220 --> 00:19:10,460
Take this money.

271
00:19:11,540 --> 00:19:12,460
I can't accept it.

272
00:19:13,780 --> 00:19:14,700
Take it.

273
00:19:15,620 --> 00:19:16,740
Buy yourself a meal,

274
00:19:17,500 --> 00:19:19,060
and get some clean clothes.

275
00:19:20,420 --> 00:19:21,940
Though we are divorced,

276
00:19:23,420 --> 00:19:25,060
you are still Yan's father.

277
00:19:26,420 --> 00:19:28,200
I won't stop you
from seeing your daughter.

278
00:19:30,090 --> 00:19:30,940
I don't want Yan

279
00:19:30,940 --> 00:19:32,220
to see her father

280
00:19:32,900 --> 00:19:34,220
like this.

281
00:19:40,180 --> 00:19:41,700
I have known you for so many years.

282
00:19:42,900 --> 00:19:44,460
I don't believe you are a bad man.

283
00:19:57,180 --> 00:20:01,780
(Fuchun Teahouse)

284
00:20:37,330 --> 00:20:40,540
♪Pink hands so fine♪

285
00:20:40,900 --> 00:20:43,760
♪Gold-branded wine♪

286
00:20:44,550 --> 00:20:50,000
♪Spring paints willows green;
palace walls can't confine♪

287
00:20:51,680 --> 00:20:55,140
♪East wind unfair♪

