00:37:53,080 --> 00:37:55,440
on the 18th day of of the 5th month,
8th year of Jingming.

580
00:37:55,500 --> 00:37:58,300
I'm in love with Zhu Ziyu,
Gentleman-Confucian.

581
00:37:58,980 --> 00:38:00,940
However, he is already married.

582
00:38:01,540 --> 00:38:03,940
I should have cut off my feelings,

583
00:38:04,220 --> 00:38:05,820
but Zhu claims his wife, Jiang,

584
00:38:06,340 --> 00:38:09,820
has met one
of the Seven Criteria for Divorce,

585
00:38:10,460 --> 00:38:13,300
and he intends to divorce her
and remarry.

586
00:38:13,700 --> 00:38:16,140
So, I set this down in writing

587
00:38:16,820 --> 00:38:18,420
that the day Zhu divorces his wife

588
00:38:19,140 --> 00:38:22,060
will be the day I marry him.

589
00:38:22,060 --> 00:38:24,980
(will be the day I marry him)

590
00:38:36,540 --> 00:38:39,780
(Contract)

591
00:38:44,450 --> 00:38:46,580
Your Majesty, please take a look.

592
00:38:49,180 --> 00:38:50,100
Rongyang,

593
00:38:50,660 --> 00:38:51,580
take a look.

594
00:38:51,780 --> 00:38:54,060
Is the handwriting the same?

595
00:38:54,460 --> 00:38:57,140
(Signed by Cui Mingyue,
Grand Princess Rongyang's daughter)

596
00:39:05,740 --> 00:39:06,740
The handwriting

597
00:39:07,700 --> 00:39:09,260
does seem similar.

598
00:39:10,620 --> 00:39:11,540
Your Majesty,

599
00:39:11,700 --> 00:39:12,660
after my examination,

600
00:39:13,300 --> 00:39:14,700
the handwriting is identical.

601
00:39:15,140 --> 00:39:17,420
They were written by the same person.

602
00:39:17,420 --> 00:39:19,340
(Contract)

603
00:39:19,340 --> 00:39:20,260
Your Majesty,

604
00:39:20,620 --> 00:39:23,040
there are many people in the world

605
00:39:23,060 --> 00:39:24,480
who can imitate others' handwriting

606
00:39:24,480 --> 00:39:25,600
and pass off fakes as real.

607
00:39:25,620 --> 00:39:27,060
If this contract were genuine,

608
00:39:27,260 --> 00:39:29,260
why did Zhu Ziyu wait until now

609
00:39:29,460 --> 00:39:31,780
to stop the ceremony in public?

610
00:39:32,660 --> 00:39:33,660
You should ask him

611
00:39:34,060 --> 00:39:36,620
who is behind all of this.

612
00:39:39,220 --> 00:39:40,140
Your Majesty,

613
00:39:40,620 --> 00:39:42,700
I didn't deliberately wait until today.

614
00:39:43,060 --> 00:39:45,060
My father was the Household Manager
of Lingshui,

615
00:39:45,620 --> 00:39:47,560
but he was falsely accused
of accepting bribes.

616
00:39:48,140 --> 00:39:49,740
My entire family was exiled.

617
00:39:51,260 --> 00:39:52,340
On the way into exile,

618
00:39:53,220 --> 00:39:54,580
we were attacked by bandits.

619
00:39:55,060 --> 00:39:57,060
Of the 83 people in our family,

620
00:39:57,460 --> 00:39:59,380
I was the only one who survived.

621
00:39:59,380 --> 00:40:00,620
What does that

622
00:40:00,740 --> 00:40:02,980
have to do with the current situation?

623
00:40:03,220 --> 00:40:04,380
After escaping death,

624
00:40:04,900 --> 00:40:06,420
I was despairing,

625
00:40:06,740 --> 00:40:08,220
only wanting to follow my family.

626
00:40:09,540 --> 00:40:11,380
It was Princess Mingyue's promise

627
00:40:11,780 --> 00:40:13,620
that gave me the hope to keep living.

628
00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:15,080
I traveled a long way to Ling'an,

629
00:40:15,080 --> 00:40:17,260
only to find that Princess Mingyue
was about to marry.

630
00:40:17,260 --> 00:40:18,540
- I was...
- Nonsense!

631
00:40:18,560 --> 00:40:20,560
Your family's disaster happened
over a month ago.

632
00:40:20,560 --> 00:40:22,500
Why did you wait until now
to arrive in Ling'an?

633
00:40:22,580 --> 00:40:24,340
Stopping a Prince's wedding alone

634
00:40:24,420 --> 00:40:26,060
is enough to sentence you to death.

635
00:40:26,340 --> 00:40:27,260
Rongyang,

636
00:40:27,460 --> 00:40:28,420
how do you know

637
00:40:29,060 --> 00:40:31,140
that it happened over a month ago?

638
00:40:38,100 --> 00:40:39,020
Your Majesty,

639
00:40:40,300 --> 00:40:41,460
I only found out

640
00:40:41,780 --> 00:40:44,020
right before entering the Palace.

641
00:40:47,940 --> 00:40:48,940
Zhen Heng,

642
00:40:49,070 --> 00:40:49,950
how do you think

643
00:40:49,960 --> 00:40:51,380
this case should be handled?

644
00:40:51,820 --> 00:40:52,740
Your Majesty,

645
00:40:53,260 --> 00:40:54,380
this contract is genuine.

646
00:40:55,020 --> 00:40:56,020
According to the law,

647
00:40:57,100 --> 00:40:58,020
Princess Mingyue

648
00:40:58,580 --> 00:41:00,060
should honor her agreement

649
00:41:00,060 --> 00:41:01,060
and marry Mr. Zhu.

650
00:41:02,340 --> 00:41:03,820
I don't want to, Uncle.

651
00:41:04,820 --> 00:41:06,660
I have deep feelings
for Princess Mingyue.

652
00:41:06,660 --> 00:41:08,040
Your Majesty, please grant my wish.

653
00:41:08,140 --> 00:41:09,020
Uncle.

654
00:41:09,020 --> 00:41:10,300
Mother, I won't marry him.

655
00:41:11,420 --> 00:41:12,980
Rongyang, look.

656
00:41:13,140 --> 00:41:15,500
As the Emperor,

657
00:41:15,500 --> 00:41:17,540
I cannot go against the law.

658
00:41:18,060 --> 00:41:19,660
Moreover, keeping one's word

659
00:41:19,660 --> 00:41:21,340
is the imperial way.

660
00:41:22,180 --> 00:41:23,300
Since it is genuine,

661
00:41:24,420 --> 00:41:25,900
Mingyue must keep her promise

662
00:41:26,340 --> 00:41:27,580
and marry Zhu Ziyu.

663
00:41:29,300 --> 00:41:30,260
No, Mother.

664
00:41:30,500 --> 00:41:31,420
I don't want to.

665
00:41:31,940 --> 00:41:33,420
I don't want to marry Zhu Ziyu.

666
00:41:33,860 --> 00:41:35,300
I want to marry Yu Jin.

667
00:41:35,300 --> 00:41:36,220
Shut up.

668
00:41:36,780 --> 00:41:39,260
If I'd known you'd been secretly engaged
to another man,

669
00:41:39,740 --> 00:41:41,140
how could I have shamelessly asked

670
00:41:41,140 --> 00:41:42,540
the Emperor for a marriage edict?

671
00:41:43,220 --> 00:41:44,680
The sins you've brought upon yourself

672
00:41:44,780 --> 00:41:46,100
are yours to bear.

673
00:41:46,820 --> 00:41:49,700
The country has its laws;
the family has its rules.

674
00:41:50,660 --> 00:41:51,580
Baoping,

675
00:41:52,220 --> 00:41:53,420
I just remembered

676
00:41:54,140 --> 00:41:55,900
the auspicious time has been set.

677
00:41:55,900 --> 00:41:58,100
Can they still marry today?

678
00:41:58,220 --> 00:41:59,300
Your Majesty,

679
00:41:59,740 --> 00:42:00,900
the auspicious time is near.

680
00:42:01,300 --> 00:42:03,860
It'd be perfect to start
the wedding ceremony now.

681
00:42:03,860 --> 00:42:04,780
Alright.

682
00:42:05,500 --> 00:42:06,980
Bring them both here.

683
00:42:07,140 --> 00:42:08,660
Today, I will witness it myself.

684
00:42:09,220 --> 00:42:10,220
Let these two couples

685
00:42:10,220 --> 00:42:11,880
have their wedding ceremony
in the Palace.

686
00:42:12,060 --> 00:42:12,980
Mother...

687
00:42:13,660 --> 00:42:15,340
Mother, please beg Uncle.

688
00:42:15,580 --> 00:42:17,420
Uncle, I beg you.

689
00:42:17,980 --> 00:42:19,860
I don't want to marry Zhu Ziyu.

690
00:42:19,860 --> 00:42:20,780
Uncle.

691
00:42:21,020 --> 00:42:23,020
- Mother, speak.
- Congratulations, Your Highness.

692
00:42:23,460 --> 00:42:24,380
Your Highness,

693
00:42:24,540 --> 00:42:26,500
His Majesty has approved your marriage.

694
00:42:26,620 --> 00:42:27,540
Go in now.

695
00:42:27,780 --> 00:42:28,700
I won't go in.

696
00:42:29,860 --> 00:42:31,180
I'm content with standing here

697
00:42:31,180 --> 00:42:32,020
