698
00:42:32,020 --> 00:42:32,940
Let's go.

699
00:42:44,100 --> 00:42:46,180
(Grand Princess's Mansion)

700
00:42:46,180 --> 00:42:47,100
Your Grace,

701
00:42:47,420 --> 00:42:48,660
