702
00:42:48,660 --> 00:42:49,780
to the Grand Princess.

703
00:42:51,340 --> 00:42:52,260
Mother,

704
00:42:52,860 --> 00:42:54,020
I'm sorry.

705
00:42:55,260 --> 00:42:57,120
I shouldn't have hidden
the contract from you,

706
00:42:57,460 --> 00:42:59,220
but I really have burned it.

707
00:42:59,340 --> 00:43:00,780
What use is there in saying this now?

